# Force LF line endings on files that downstream tools parse as YAML
# or shell scripts. cc-symphony's YAML parser (rust/serde-yaml) treats
# CRLF in some positions as malformed input and fails with
#   "invalid type: unit value, expected path string"
# at startup. Verified 2026-05-08 against cc-symphony 0.1.0.

WORKFLOW.md text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
